nodes.text: Ian Whyte (born September 17, 1971) is an actor who portrayed various creature characters in Star Wars: Episode VII The Force Awakens and Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, including Bollie Prindel, Moroff and Roodown. He is credited as a puppeteer for these films.
He is best know for his roles in Prometheus, the Alien vs. Predator films, and Game of Thrones.
